<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Your Password - Model Scout Pro</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 0.8em;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= firstName %>,</h2>
      <p>
        We received a request to reset your password for your Model Scout Pro
        account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this
        email.
      </p>
      <p>To reset your password, please click the button below:</p>
      <a href="<%= url %>" class="button">Reset Your Password</a>
      <p>This link will expire in 10 minutes for security reasons.</p>
      <p>
        If the button above doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the
        following link into your browser:
      </p>
      <p><%= url %></p>
      <p>
        If you have any issues or didn't request this password reset, please
        contact our support team immediately.
      </p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The Model Scout Pro Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Model Scout Pro. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p>
        This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this
        email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
